an updated document. And this is how I consider this whole process is we're trying to take the structure and the framework of what we have and make it more understandable and readable and modern so that then when we have our comprehensive plan and when we have discussions around equity, we can go into it and know exactly where we need to go, what definitions do we need to look at, which sections do we need to look at. But I think that feedback.

31
00:11:36,530 --> 00:11:52,207
is still valuable even before that, as we pass this element of just getting us to a modern and readable zoning ordinance. And really, I think

